0x3F3EB3F7// OverrideReactionToVehicleSiren
void OVERRIDE_REACTION_TO_VEHICLE_SIREN(BOOL state, int reaction);Parameters:state: Toggle on or offreaction: Decide how they should reactSetting the state to true and a value between 0 and 2 will cause pedestrian vehicles to react accordingly to sirens.enum Reactions {
    Left = 0,
    Right = 1,
    Stop = 2
}
